title: Ivanti Neurons for MDM (formerly MobileIron Cloud): Device compliance
agents: mobileiron
catalog: app/ivantineurons
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 The special agent Ivanti Neurons for MDM (formerly MobileIron Cloud) 
 queries the cloud instance through the REST API.

 This check monitors the compliance state of each device managed via Ivanti Neurons for MDM.

 The service state depends on the number of policy violations
 and the compliance state of the device and can be configured.
 The default parameters are: {WARN} for 2 policy violations and {CRIT} for 3.

discovery:
 One service per device is created
